			<p>Dear &lt;salutation&gt;</p>
			<p align="center"><b>Would you like to take some of the worry out of next Christmas?</b></p><br>
			<p>With so much to do and so much to pay for at Christmas, it can be a very stressful time. If you agree, we can help take some of that stress away…..starting right now.</p>
			<p>Morses Club’s range of over 130 Christmas Hampers include a great of food, drink and freezer hampers that we can help you to save for in advance and deliver right to your door.</p>
			<p>Once you have made your choice, your representative will set up an account for you into which your weekly savings are paid. Then, in good time for Christmas, we will arrange delivery of your hamper directly to your home at a time to suit you.</p>
			<p align="center"><b>...And win a 28&quot; Digital TV or DVD Player with Freeview</b></p>
			<p>Morses Club are also giving you the opportunity to enter a prize draw to win a 28&quot; Digital TV or a DVD player with Freeview. Full terms and conditions can be found on the 2005 Hamper Order form.</p>
			<p align="center"><b>What to do next</b></p>
			<p>If you’re interested in finding out more about our range of Hampers, just talk to your Representative who will give you a copy of our 2005 Hamper Brochure and tell you everything you need to know.</p>
